Yum! I'm a pretty inexperienced cook, so I was pleasantly surprised at how easy this was to make. I used orange bell peppers and I didn't peel them, but everything turned out great. Balsamic with zucchini is quickly becoming my new favorite thing to eat. The flavor was sweeter here than just sauteing it like I usually do.